snippet.title: HUGEL feat. Amber Van Day - Mamma Mia (Official Video)
snippet.description:
The official music video for HUGEL's new single "Mamma Mia" feat. Amber van Day! 
Get the track here: http://wmg.click/Hugel_MammaMiaAY 

HUGEL - Warner Music
French DJ Producer Songwriter 

Social Media: Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/hugelthug/

Picture a hot night in the club, the party machinery is running at full speed and with every progressing hour, people are letting their hair down a little more. Let’s briefly sum up tonight’s impressions so far, shall we: “Ass, titties, shots, ass, titties, drink”. And now this: a monster drop, hitting you right in the face and obliterating the dancefloor for a brief moment of eternity. 

Welcome to “Mamma Mia”, the new single by HUGEL. Said lyrics can actually be heard in the song, delivered by Amber Van Day, who already featured in his last smasher “WTF”. Once again, her sexy, self-assured doesn’t fail to impress. Which is also owed to the song’s explicit lyrics, of course. In “Mamma Mia”, HUGEL takes a dig at the shallow consumer- and party culture he witnesses every day playing the world’s top clubs. The world, he seems to tell us, is material and shallow. So let’s at least have a good party!

An outrageously good funk sample by James Brown, Prince-esque guitar licks and a wind section make for the foundation of this song, soon culminating in a foghorn drop you won’t get out of your head. Just like that Gucci bag you saw in that boutique earlier. Or was it Balenciaga? Doesn’t matter: “Gucci Gang (Na na na) / Diamonds on me (Na na na) / More champagne papi”, Amber Van Day reminds us that our glass is empty yet again. Refill and proceed!
